		"description": "<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-fcbaf624-7fff-1dc4-8984-9e41fecd6949\" dir=\"ltr\">You are quick of study and always on the lookout for new teachers. You require only half the usual gold and time to perform the Research downtime activity. In addition, after speaking with a person for at least 1 minute, you can use an action to make either an Insight or Arcana check against their passive Deception. On a success, you learn the following information about them:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Whether they have a higher Intelligence score than yourself.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Which lore skills (Arcana, Culture, Engineering, History, Nature, and Religion) they are proficient in, if any.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Whether they have class levels in the warlock or wizard class.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
